  messages:
  - 'Lyra Durand is a detective who specializes in the past. She solves the various
    requests that come her way by speaking with ghosts to uncover their mysteries
    and help the citizens deal with the supernatural. Today, she finds herself at
    the Encore Mansion for a new case. '
